  "title": "Wealth Manager ($5,000/ No need experience) PP",
  "description": "<p><em><strong>Perks</strong></em></p><ul><li>Attractive remuneration and a comprehensive benefits package</li><li>Overseas incentive trips</li><li>Structured training and on-the-job training to help you develop the skillsets you need</li><li>Hybrid work mode available</li></ul><p><strong>Job Details:</strong></p><ul><li>Research and recommend prospects for new business opportunities.</li><li>Meet with potential clients to determine their needs.</li><li>Build and maintain relationships with clients and prospects.</li><li>Stay current with trends and competitors to identify improvements or recommend new products.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Local Diploma/ Any Degree qualification</li><li>No experience required</li><li>Extrovert with good communication skills</li><li>Sales motivated to earn a higher income</li></ul><p><br /></p><p><strong>Click 'APPLY NOW' to proceed.</strong></p><p><br /></p><p>We regret that only short-listed candidates will be contacted.</p><p><br /></p><p>EA License: 22C1201</p><p>EA Reg Number: R1325831</p>",
